{
  "texts": [
    "The given scheme monitors the behavior of every node as normal or abnormal.",
    "The authors linked these nodes to a Bayesian network that plays an important role in the detection of potential abnormal behaviors of any NDN node.",
    "The work and design of the propose scheme consist of a monitoring plan and a data plan, as shown in Fig. 17.",
    "The monitoring plan consists of a Micro Detector, a Correlation Engine Bayesian Network, and a Montimage Monitoring Tool (MMT).",
    "The Micro Detector uses a constant Rate of False Alarms (RFA) to determine whether the metrics are in a normal or abnormal state."
  ]
}